org.csstudio.platform.internal.developmentsupport.util
Class DummyContentModelProvider

java.lang.Object
  org.csstudio.platform.internal.developmentsupport.util.DummyContentModelProvider

public final class DummyContentModelProvider
extends Object

Maintains a dummy model for the resources view. The initial model is a simple list, that contains some workspace projects as well as some process variables. Additional model objects can be contributed.

Author:
Sven Wende
